On Mon, 22 Sep 2008, Ahlgrim, Kevin wrote:

> am looking for suggestions as to making
> sure the mouse is gone and how to keep them out.  We're going camping this
> coming weekend and I don't want to wake up next to anything other than my
> wife.  Thanks for any help you can give me. Kevin

Nothing like a good old-fashioned mouse trap baited with peanut butter.

I keep a couple in the garage all the time to catch the mice before they
decide to reproduce.  It's better than poison since you really don't want
a mouse to crawl somewhere inaccessable in your bus to expire.
